Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Academy city is in high spirits from the Daihaseisai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.94,0:00:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using that chance, a ceremonial item, the Stab Sword, which can slay a saint in one strike, is being transacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of the carrier is Oriana Thomson.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By coincidence, I came into contact with a person who resembled her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently,{Right now} we are heading to places which Oriana might use to carry out the transaction-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, the moment I shook hands with her{made a handshake with a person},
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my imagine breaker dispelled something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it was though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't look like a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.88,0:02:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't she carry something big with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she had something that looked like a road sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm currently tailing her.{I'm following after her.} {I'm chasing her.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll send you the GPS coordinates of this location{place}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do a search on your side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She noticed me following her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That blond woman wearing a factory work outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two seem to be professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told they can't use force inside the city areas,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess they won't go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her movements are somewhat weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she change her mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bus terminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.37,0:03:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the maintenance yard for automated buses.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.60,0:03:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's where you show your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I must say that was some excellent teamwork. {a well coordinated assult?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to take action if our roles are well defined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you-!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So go serve your purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.36,0:04:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl, place your rune cards and stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will take the carrier down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do, Kami-yan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe it's probably safer for you to stay here though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too, believe it's safer that you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is, it becomes safe for me, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are just decoys to keep us busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:05:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll let her escape if we take countermeasures against all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you told me that...{You can just tell me that though...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oriana Thomson, the Route Disturb...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a joke out of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I also owe you an apology.{Oh no, rather I am the one who should be sorry.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This spell is a Rihashijin Circle.{logical fraction four circle}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will search for Oriana's position using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't it be bad for you if you use magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.83,0:06:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm going to ask for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Communicate through the wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to the air, but communicate the intention to the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Communicate through the wind, "
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not to the air, but communicate the intention to the field."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.29,0:07:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit Stiyl's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A type of counter magic against tracing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there are no such artifacts of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was probably a counter response magic already set to fire when it identifies your individual magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it means Stiyl can't use magic against Oriana anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an annoying magic she cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.13,0:08:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With {only? }one body she is detecting vital signs, analyzing it, reversing assembly, application and even counter action...from "Route Disturb".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Route Disturb"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oriana Thomson's nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But anyways, I seem to recall this way of doing things that seems to lack any sense of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine she would have that.{she would have what that?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No Stiyl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had the same thoughts{idea} too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if that's so, then that means she isn't a magician, but a wizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you{is the thing you are} talking about? {What the fuck are you talking about?}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With knowledge of magic stuffed into an object,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it emits a magic circle by itself, without needing a spellcaster to take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.84,0:08:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the original intent of a magic book.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But creating magic books depending on the situation is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While they are originals, they are written sloppily. {quick way of writting, so it's really looking... unreadable, but its readable.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should only have limited effects and break down quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:09:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that would be called Short Hand, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what do we have to do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.87,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First we destroy the auto counter-attack spell, allowing Stiyl to use his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How high is the possibility that she'd escape beyond search range while we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.13,0:09:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she was confident that she could escape immediately, she wouldn't have to cast a counter spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you believe so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl, cast something, anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senjutsu Enjin.{fortune telling(psychic/divination?) circle; lets keep it as japanese, lol.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an unused magic circle which has had no one's magical powers been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will start detecting the counter spells and figure out the direction and distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.64,0:09:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tsuchimikado, if you execute something like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiyl will once more be-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once more?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.87,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't find the position of the Short Hands, we will have to have him try as many times. {we will have him try until we got all of 'em?}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, since you seem to have forgotten, I'll remind you of one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a battle that we risk lives for.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the outcome, countries and even the world's fate could be affected greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go with that plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit the friendly-cosy attitude, Kamijou Touma.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that lets us finish everything, then there's nothing wrong with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.56,0:10:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the position of the counter spell, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defending Index's life at Academy City at all cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that was the condition, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not happy that you are here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you not by her side?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If her face becomes unhappy because of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.42,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.86,0:11:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I went through all the trouble of changing just to see Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to have just run off on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister-chan, don't get so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.23,0:11:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou-chan must have had a very good reason to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.79,0:11:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disappearing the second I let my eyes off him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing out here in public?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's confused, we can use a stimulant such as red pepper to distract her-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No she's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's absolutely fine, Fukiyose-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touma...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.74,0:11:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Touma go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it shows up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a response from the Senjutsu Enjin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Kami-yan, don't you have a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there's a GPS map on my mobile phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so cold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think Stiyl was injured for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, he's a professional magician too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has some resistance to magic attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Senjutsu Enjin reacts to magic power that comes shooting through, and tells you the direction and distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way such a useful article can be used without using magic power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.83,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could properly use magic, Stiyl wouldn't have had to suffer like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would admit that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hate me as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will surely find the Short Hands, and destroy them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I will also find Oriana, and stop the transaction of{screw} the Stab Sword with my very own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out what is there 302 meters to the Northwest of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Short Hands should be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A middle school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The stadium?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.09,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time left before it starts! {No time left before it's starting!}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's guests, and even the camera is in already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do it secretly anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't leave it as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will have to sneak in as competitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you seriously saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're high school students, you know?  {'ya kno~?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to mix in with middle school-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:14:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That counter spell might hit bystanders as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.62,0:14:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what the easiest castable spell in this world is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even people who can't cast magic can cause the counter spell to react by merely touching.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.67,0:14:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And due to them having no magical defence ability, it'll get really dangerous if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway Kami-yan, we need to get rid of that counter spell before there are any victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.83,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our event is coming up next, are we going to have to show up dressed like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cameras are rolling too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have spare gym uniforms{suits}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, I have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're still in the clubhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, go change quickly then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{Since it's the rule}I'll have to check your ID in accordance to the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimika...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your hand before using it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.07,0:15:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine then, go in already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't allow you to participate after it begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we can't mix in the event dressed like this-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it's known that they have spare gym uniforms{suits} in the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next even is the ball throwing battle between the 200 handpicked members of Minamisawa Middle School against...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.50,0:15:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 handpicked members of Tokiwadai Middle School.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They reek of a lost battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.60,0:16:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How smelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Tokiwadai Middle School?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have scary ability users over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should watch out for stray shots Kami-yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she would have set up a Short Hand, where would it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, I think the baskets are suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be ones borrowed from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could have set them up before they were brought in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check the baskets one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.44,0:16:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, it's your job after I find the Short Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On your mark,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready, set,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.87,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be startled!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're breaking through, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.14,0:17:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miss, Kami-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move on to the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.19,0:17:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, it's not this one either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, use my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.50,0:18:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,really want to punish me so badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Misaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Misaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll properly tell you the reason later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So get away from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.82,0:18:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you telling me all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.57,0:18:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you even here in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain that to me first-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit getting in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Misaka, can you please come over here without asking any questions{ask no more and come this way}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.55,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have solved it without your help anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you need to talk about{is the talk you have} anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.36,0:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'll tell you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you to be injured!{misakamisakamisakamisakamisakaaaaaargghhhhhhhh}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be so worried about me in an event like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, don't surprise me by suddenly telling me something really strange like that-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay still for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.68,0:20:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it hurt that much, Misaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your fever-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuchimikado, the pole over here has-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijou Touma, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you running off in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, we're going to restart the event.{the event will be restarted from the beginning.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kami-yan, hit Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not a magician. {She is no magician.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, her body won't last any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.02,0:21:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Oriana Thomson,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is your way of doing things,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After getting a countless number of innocent people involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you don't feel anything after doing that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.79,0:21:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will completely destroy{your senseless illusion,},
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{I will kill without trace}your senseless illusion with my very own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukiyose collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.31,0:23:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So did Stiyl and Tsuchimikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.68,0:23:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Stab Sword was the cause of this battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.85,0:23:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely break that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.81,0:23:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, Short Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When science and magic cross, the story begins.
